import React from 'react'; function DataElement(props) { return(
Nome do Pokemon setName(e.target.value)} type="text" />
Level setLevel(e.target.value)} type="text" />
IVs (Para cada atributo: Min: 0 Max: 31)
Hp: setHpIv(e.target.value)} type='text'/> Atk: setAttackIv(e.target.value)} type='text'/> Def: setDefenseIv(e.target.value)} type='text'/> Sp Atk: setSpAttackIv(e.target.value)} type='text'/> Sp Def: setSpDefenseIv(e.target.value)} type='text'/> Speed: setSpeedIv(e.target.value)} type='text'/>
EVs (Para cada atributo: Min: 0 Max: 255)
Hp: setHpEv(e.target.value)} type='text'/> Atk: setAttackEv(e.target.value)} type='text'/> Def: setDefenseEv(e.target.value)} type='text'/> Sp Atk: setSpAttackEv(e.target.value)} type='text'/> Sp Def: setSpDefenseEv(e.target.value)} type='text'/> Speed: setSpeedEv(e.target.value)} type='text'/>
); } export default DataElement;
